title: Kate OBrien
text: Kate O’Brien is a student of Marine Science with a minor in Data Science at [California State University, Monterey Bay](https://csumb.edu/marinescience/).

title: About
text: Hi, my name is Kate OBrien and I’m a current student in my second year at CSU Monterey Bay. I’m majoring in Marine Science, with a minor in data science. I’m passionate about conservation, and have a strong desire to protect our beautiful oceans and natural resources. I’ve also been an active scuba diver for nearly a year, and am currently in the process of getting my master diver certification.
